{"tid":2050174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美媒揭WHO怨中國拖延公布資訊　世衛官員未否認","createTime":"2020-06-04T03:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T06:34:08.000Z","uid":19552,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"84fc72f7c3981f8249dad704d6e0fb7b40ea229c","tid":2050174,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:11:48.000Z","msg":"WHO雖然屢次在公開場合「感謝」中國分享武漢肺炎疫情資訊，但美聯社近日取得WHO的內部文件和錄音檔，顯示WHO官員曾多次私底下抱怨中國分享的資料不足、遲遲不公布基因序列，令WHO難以評估病毒能有效人傳人的程度，白白浪費寶貴的時間。為了哄勸中國政府提供更多資訊，WHO官員只好公開讚揚中國。<br />\n 。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\nWHO周三在每日例行的疫情記者會上，被媒體問到WHO對這則報導的評論，「當事人」萊恩沒有直接回應提問，也沒有否認報導內容，而是看著文稿，簡短表示WHO領導層及員工皆依照相關規章，日以繼夜與會員國共享訊息及與各政府進行坦率對話，並說這就是他的說明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200604/VGBH6AE7JFCOZQ3YXHNLKF2TEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200604%2FVGBH6AE7JFCOZQ3YXHNLKF2TEQ%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=6f537c74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200604%2FVGBH6AE7JFCOZQ3YXHNLKF2TEQ%2F&h=d332be1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200604/VGBH6AE7JFCOZQ3YXHNLKF2TEQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f85f30323e77b3c3abdf270119c709e02692767e","tid":2050174,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"WHO D 人會唔會要負刑事責任<br />\n唯有幫支那食左隻死貓啦。"},{"pid":"ac6a00df863eece9a07f7265d3755df04839e388","tid":2050174,"uid":128178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:21:07.000Z","msg":"為了哄勸中國政府提供更多資訊，WHO官員只好公開讚揚中國。<br />\n<br />\n哩個係咩logic？？"},{"pid":"558b6b02faf639bb903460c27747d2d1ff8627e3","tid":2050174,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac6a00df863eece9a07f7265d3755df04839e388","tid":2050174,"uid":128178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:21:07.000Z","msg":"為了哄勸中國政府提供更多資訊，WHO官員只好公開讚揚中國。<br />\n<br />\